sentences.english: How many men do you know who eat low-calorie or fat-free anything ?
sentences.chinese: 看看有幾個男人專喫低熱或者去脂食品？

sentences.chinese: 遞交評定報告或證書關於專利廠防火閘的安裝方法。

sentences.english: Now the army meals have improved and are already rather different from having only pickles to eat.
sentences.chinese: 現在部隊的伙食改善了，已經比專喫酸菜有所不同了。

sentences.english: Study on the specificity in the transmission of plant virus by vector nematodes has made great progress.
sentences.chinese: 介體線蟲傳播植物病毒專化性的研究已取得很大進展。

sentences.english: Actually, it's simply a very author_itarian, dictat_orial polit_ical regime.
sentences.chinese: 事實上它是一種非常獨C專Z的鄭智體制。

sentences.english: The bird feeds on cliff-top vegetation.
sentences.chinese: 這種鳥專喫懸崖頂上的植物。

sentences.english: Bayi's hens always ate the poor people's millet.
sentences.chinese: 巴依的雞專喫窮人的穀子。

sentences.english: This module makes it possible to transfer requests to another server.
sentences.chinese: 此模塊專伺將請求導向其它服務。

sentences.english: They were monotheists, devoted to the God of Israel.
sentences.chinese: 他們是一神論者，專致於以色列的神。

sentences.english: Every item shall include a standard complement of accessories and special tools to ensure the normal operation.
sentences.chinese: 證設備正常運轉，每品目都應括套標準額附件專。

sentences.english: The heckler was ejected from the meeting.
sentences.chinese: 那個專找茬兒的搗蛋分子被逐出會場。

sentences.english: Market concentration is not high, the production of special automobile enterprises is not special"."
sentences.chinese: 市場集中度不高，專用汽車企業生產不“專”。
